Class Latitude

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs350f20project.datatype.A_LatitudeLongitude
      • cs350f20project.datatype.Latitude
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<A_LatitudeLongitude>

    public class Latitude
extends A_LatitudeLongitude
    Defines latitude encoded in NMEA 0183 format. It works only in the Northern Hemisphere. For example, Spokane International Airport lies roughly at 47°37'8".
